description: Product packaging:Beautiful packaging box500 pieces puzzleMesh bagDetachable partition partitionPicture posterPuzzle combination method:1.Prepare a thick cardboard or tabletop that is larger than the size of the puzzle.Before the puzzle is combined,cushion it underneath to facilitate the movement and collection during the assembly process,and to prevent the puzzle from being scattered and lost.2.First take out the pieces on the four sides of the puzzle: one side is a straight line,and both sides are straight.Then combine the four sides of the picture and then proceed to the center of the picture to reduce the time of the puzzle.3.When combining,if the jigsaw and the jigsaw puzzle can't be tightly tight,or the hue is different(especially when dealing with the same color system,you need to pay attention to it),don't force the combination, please take some effort to find the correct number of pieces.There are English numbers on the back of the puzzle,which makes it easy to complete the puzzle.This puzzle is made of high quality wood with corrosion and wear resistance.(Please try to avoid water,if there is water splashing on the puzzle,please wipe the water as soon as possible)Puzzles are a meaningful game or activity that adds a bit of fun to your irritating heart and boring spare time.And after you finish it,you will be very fulfilled and can also be used as a home decor!If you are looking for a gift from a child or a friend, I think you should need it!
